c: 39
v: 7
t: "'iina tkfru- 'ayuha alnas- birabikum walam tuminuu bh, walam tatabieuu rslh, fa'iinah ghny enkm, lays bihajat 'ilykm, wa'antum alfuqara' 'ilyh, wala yardaa lieibadih alkfr, wala yamuruhum bh, wa'iinama yardaa lahum shakar nieamah elyhm. wala tahmil nfs 'iithm nfs akhra, thuma 'iilaa rabukum msyrkm, fykhbrkm bemlkm, wyhasbkm elyh. 'iinah ealim bi'asrar alnufus wama tukhfi alsdwr"